    "description" : "Short description: Load error logs from sequential files using file pattern into F20_EXCP_LOG table. Long description: Load error logs from sequential files using file pattern into F20_EXCP_LOG table.\r\n\r\nCreated by: Marcin Szablewski\r\nCreation date: 2013-02-15\r\n\r\nModified by: SEDC\r\nModification date: 2014-05-13\r\n\r\nV0.1 (Marcin Szablewski) : Loads process logs from sequential files into  F20_EXCP_LOG using pattern. Logs are created by the error handling component.\r\n\r\nV0.2 (Denis Leroy) :\r\nChange into a Parallel job.\r\nSeq file set to \"pattern\"\r\nTransformer is BASIC transformer\r\n\r\nV1.0 (SEDC) :\r\nAlignment with the new EH version.\r\nColumns datatypes.\r\nNew parameter PM_RUN_ID.\r\n\r\nV1.1 (SEDC) :\r\nPrecision alignment with the database.\r\nValidation of PM_RUN_ID parameter.\r\n\r\nV1.2 (SEDC) :\r\nMapping of invalid characters.\r\n\r\nV1.3 (SEDC) :\r\nUpdate ErrorAdditionalInfo column length.\r\n",
